{"tid":2191402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新巴正了解巴士司機被帶走事件　警稱司機作出挑釁行為無故響咹，影響警方工作，亦會挑起在場人士的情緒","createTime":"2020-09-06T12:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T12:16:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63991f23737f2fd24efb6910095a076f93b03faa","tid":2191402,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T12:05:22.000Z","msg":"警方社交網站的直播片段所見，多名警員下午在油麻地包圍該輛970號巴士，要求司機下車。片段中，一名警員表示，警方在文明里附近進行截查工作期間，該名司機向警方作出挑釁行為、無故響咹，影響警方工作，亦會挑起在場人士的情緒。有警員表示，司機的駕駛行為及態度 ，對道路使用者造成危險，是危險駕駛。警員之後將該名司機帶上警車。<br />\n<br />\n新巴回覆查詢表示，下午約4時半，一名車長駕駛970號線往數碼港方向期間，在彌敦道近文明里被警方要求離開駕駛室，及後被帶往警署，正在了解事件詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548172-20200906.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548172-20200906.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4ohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=afc8e405\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548172-20200906.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c4920522\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548172-20200906.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c2a50298ca8f61ba58ae1a6c45ac4de9ae48a648","tid":2191402,"uid":53666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"惡過皇軍<br />\n<br />\n仲唔下跪"},{"pid":"8e9b449a99b26d027ca551b6e5135adba49ad902","tid":2191402,"uid":288675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T12:11:01.000Z","msg":"唔日日去紅隧拉人？"},{"pid":"929dca3e7f0ee1bd1cb88c4914ec89697b5e3a97","tid":2191402,"uid":126133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T12:16:55.000Z","msg":"警謊又話暴徒堵路<br />\n佢響咹諗住驅趕啲暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知有人爭住認啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪"}]}